{"tid":688702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又跪地又騎牛牛？馬場巴士迷小朋友齊打交！","createTime":"2018-06-03T12:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:44:09.000Z","uid":46896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d476b7aee18b6e0e77959b22c34cf00b9542961a","tid":688702,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:48:11.000Z","msg":"沙田馬場從來是巴士迷的是非之地，繼去年9月有巴士迷在馬場巴士站粗口橫飛兼出手後，今日（3日）又有巴士迷在拍攝馬場巴士時大打出手。網上流出的連環圖顯示，3名少年未知何故，在巴士站附近的空地起爭執，一名紅衣少年疑在跪地求饒，但仍被另外一名少年按在地上打，另一人則在旁附和叫囂。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今日下午，紅衣少年被白衣惡少騎住，再壓在地上，臉向地面。據現場消息指，事件中3人均為巴士迷，被打少年最終被打至出血。有人直指事件涉及巴士迷欺凌，呼籲警方徹查。<br />\n<br />\n巴士迷已不是首次在沙田馬場起爭執。2017年9月馬季開鑼日，至少20名十多歲的巴士迷傍晚在拍攝巴士時，疑有人因故意阻礙其他人拍照，而被其他巴士迷圍住，並以粗口指罵，最終需要警員到場調停，有巴士迷慨嘆:「成個香港巴迷界被你搞『彎』晒啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180603201831\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180603201831&h=98310988&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180603201831\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180603201831&h=c02fa0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180603201831\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180603201831&h=410ac587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_04p.jpg?20180603201831\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20180603201831&h=7012f2f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e86253819c39461a069760e993bad9931fe2037","tid":688702,"uid":29070,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"又係啲垃圾巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61241419fd8622d1a630f6c8239f0659a5029bf4","tid":688702,"uid":137604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/210706_680f41a7f4120c6736410985084e416c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F210706_680f41a7f4120c6736410985084e416c.jpeg&h=e0d9c3a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bebfb823b7d2d8c29160c098259bda2fe671da9f","tid":688702,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"巴膠好仔黎<br />\n好專一架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece6e75ffb13cf2e4710729b811f9edf7c364426","tid":688702,"uid":3647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"一係好似我以前細個咁<br />\n一路騎牛牛 一路打pat pat<br />\n<br />\n唔好呀 大王"},{"pid":"1e308c9aa83ecb2f62e6d2fe2c26e514ab5bdfa5","tid":688702,"uid":151955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"好迷唔迷走去迷巴士，比幾蚊都有得你上，有乜撚野好迷，都白撚痴痴"},{"pid":"d90a746b1a9af3d65380f6f4643e33fb5106141e","tid":688702,"uid":3457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1e308c9aa83ecb2f62e6d2fe2c26e514ab5bdfa5","tid":688702,"uid":151955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"好迷唔迷走去迷巴士，比幾蚊都有得你上，有乜撚野好迷，都白撚痴痴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"成班毒撚黎🤣🤣🤣 小朋友齊打架 <br />\n記得之前有片睇佢地鬧交 有人拎自己幾早到影巴士黎拎優越感😂😂😂😂<br />\n笑撚到我肚痛 <br />\n巴膠 鐵膠 真係毒撚中既經典 <br />\n一個屌死氣喉 一個屌幕門🙊"},{"pid":"2b43a75a14f00f212485f26390fae17f12908bfa","tid":688702,"uid":82532,"like":0,"di